        'Find permanent housing (SeLoger, LeBonCoin, PAP)',
        'Apply for Titre de séjour (residence permit) at préfecture if needed',
        'Register for CAF (housing benefit) if eligible',
        'Set up utilities (EDF, Engie, internet)',
        'Join expat communities (InterNations Paris, Meetup)',
        'Register with your home country embassy (optional)'
      ],
      phase4Extra: [
        'Complete probation milestones (période d\'essai)',
        'File tax registration with Service des impôts',
        'Get permanent phone plan',
