        'Get skills assessment from relevant authority',
        'Arrange health insurance or check Medicare eligibility',
        'Get police clearance certificate from home country'
      ],
      phase2: [
        'Apply for TFN (Tax File Number) online at ATO website',
        'Open Australian bank account (Commonwealth, ANZ, Westpac, NAB)',
        'Get Australian SIM card (Telstra, Optus, Vodafone)',
        'Enroll in Medicare (if eligible on your visa)',
        'Apply for tax file number if not done online',
        'Get Opal card / Myki / Go card for public transport'
      ],
      phase3: [
        'Find permanent housing (Domain, realestate.com.au, Flatmates)',
        'Register with local council',
